程序包 nbaquery.data
的使用

  • nbaquery.data使用的nbaquery.data中的类 
    类和说明
    Column
    Providing services of modifying and accessing rows in the table.
    DirtyDataInfo
    A record of the dirty data, containing the info, like in which table, on which row, to which column, and what dirty data occurs.
    Row
    A certain row in the table, containing certain data of the row.
    Table
    Providing services of accessing rows and columns in the table.
    TableHost
    The owner of the tables, providing services of creating tables, from system start-up, or user performed query.
